{"type": "article", "id": 10606, "title": "Rain Lamp吊灯", "description": "", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235812BZrQGdktELJDUbhf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 <a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Richard Clarkson Studio</a> 的一个叫做和谐与矛盾系列的第一个作品，将电和水这对似乎不能共存的元素组合起来。这盏灯使用水和微型蠕动泵系统创造一种闪烁的波纹。球状的内部使LED灯光投射到地面上有放大的效果，微型泵使 Rain Lamp底部的水源源不断地循环滴下，并且灯光折射会在地面上形成不同的涟漪。(<a href=\"http://www.richardclarkson.com/rain\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里访问官网</a>）<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235810CYpal3W7hNRtO2z8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235810ds2QkOEXZGyeFpln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052358112fKmSwWOxDycZCq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052358112kIfqYeOD0FTZu9i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}